Ivan Laughlin WAGNER, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 11610. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit Oct. 23, 1946. Ivan Laughlin Wagner, of Leavenworth, Kansas, in pro. per., for appellant. John D. Hill, U. S. Atty., of Birmingham, Ala., for appellee.

Before HOLMES, McCORD, and LEE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The motion to dismiss is overruled and the judgment affirmed.
